<tr>
<td><b>Spirochete:</b>
<p><i>Treponema pallidum</i>
<ul>
<li>
first observed by Fritz Schaudinn (1871-1906) in March 1905</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>
fragile organism</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>
must be transferred through intimate contact</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>
reproduces slowly -- divides every 30 hours compared to every 20-30 minutes
for most bacteria</li>
</ul>
</td>

<td BGCOLOR="#184B81"><div align="center"><img SRC="spirocheteb.jpg" BORDER=0 height=472 width=300></div></td>
</tr>
</table>



